"{\"uid\": \"thegatewaypundit.com-2024-05-remarkable-walmart-deli-worker-qualifies-u-s-olympic\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  A Walmart Deli worker has qualified for the U.S. Olympic track and field trials in Eugene, Oregon.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 93, \"end\": 99, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.9498771973854587, \"rank\": 0.05274407191717739, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HurdlerDylan Beardqualified for the Olympic trials after placing first in the 60m hurdles at the Millrose Games in February.\", \"from\": 102, \"to\": 226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike other Olympic athletes who train full-time and are sponsored, Beard is not sponsored yet and supports himself by working as a deli worker at Walmart.\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 376, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walmart\", \"score\": 0.9999999993731308, \"rank\": 6.269555869782354e-10, \"text\": \"Walmart\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walmart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walmart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beard's Walmart manager, David Davis, shared, \\\"Dylan's work ethic is next level.\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 394, \"end\": 401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walmart\", \"score\": 0.9999999993731308, \"rank\": 6.269555869782354e-10, \"text\": \"Walmart\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walmart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walmart\"}, {\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Davis_(British_politician)\", \"score\": 0.792380661317513, \"rank\": 0.23920660036167665, \"text\": \"David Davis\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Davis_(British_politician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Davis_(British_politician)\"}, {\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"score\": 0.9999799843701559, \"rank\": 1.1076019626088181e-05, \"text\": \"Dylan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He provides excellent customer service all the time.\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He goes above and beyond, just like he does on the track.\\\"\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the Top Olympic Hopefuls Trains Between His Shifts as a Deli Counter Worker at Walmarthttps://t.co/2EkS8tZwxV  - People (@people)April 26, 2024    PerAOL:  Beard is a hurdler who will compete for a spot on the United States Olympic team heading to the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.5143893096427081, \"rank\": 0.48762276913339836, \"text\": \"United States Olympic team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996714289494, \"rank\": 3.2857116290278525e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also happens to work a full-time job at the deli counter at a Walmart.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walmart\", \"score\": 0.9999999993731308, \"rank\": 6.269555869782354e-10, \"text\": \"Walmart\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walmart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walmart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beard emerged as a surprise winner while competing in the 60-meter hurdles at the Millrose Games in February.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I went in a lot more relaxed, like nothing to lose, a lot to gain,\\\" he told TODAY in an interview that aired April 26.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His performance in the race made him the third fastest hurdler in the world and landed him a spot at the U.S. Olympic track and field trials in Eugene, Oregon, in June.\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.9498771973854587, \"rank\": 0.05274407191717739, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following his performance at the Millrose Games, Beard returned to his normal routine.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's Beard in action:  An unsponsored Walmart deli worker is a contender for the#ParisOlympics.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Make no mistake - Dylan Beard is legit.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1559, \"end\": 1564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"score\": 0.9999799843701559, \"rank\": 1.1076019626088181e-05, \"text\": \"Dylan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\"